 code and UI design that avoids generic AI aesthetics.","license":"Complete terms in LICENSE.txt"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"00_System/Links/Agent_Skills_Global/frontend-design/SKILL.md"},
